Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00bfff&}양손을 잡아줘요
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.48,0:27:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00bfff&}이윽고 오는 미래로
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.11,0:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00bfff&}그날 여름 봤던 꿈
